---
title: Curried Cauliflower & Potatoes with Green Peas
description: This one-pot Indian-inspired dish doesn't rely on curry powder alone for punch. We've amped up the flavor profile with extra coriander, cumin, and Thai chili for bite. The best part? You'll have just one pan to clean by the end of the recipe. Oh, and another bonus - leftovers taste even better the next day.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54ecdadf6ced6e41738b4568.jpg
